code: @Override protected RestChannelConsumer prepareRequest(final RestRequest request, final NodeClient client) throws IOException {     final String id = request.param("id").     final PutRollupJobAction.Request putRollupJobRequest = PutRollupJobAction.Request.fromXContent(request.contentParser(), id).     return channel -> client.execute(PutRollupJobAction.INSTANCE, putRollupJobRequest, new RestToXContentListener<>(channel)). }
